Lenovo Chief Yuanqing Borrowed to Buy Company Stock

-- B y   M a r k   L e e
-- 
2011-08-18T03:36:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/lenovo-chief-yuanqing-borrowed-to-buy-company-stock-correct-.html
(Corrects spelling on Yuanqing in headline.)  Lenovo Group Ltd. (992)  Chief Executive
Officer  Yang Yuanqing  took on personal loans to buy company
shares in June, Chairman Liu Chuanzhi said in a conference call
today. Yang’s investment displayed his confidence in the company
and “a long term mentality,” Liu said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
